Hi. I'm OrienST8. You may call me w/e you want, does not matter much to me.

~Current Skill Gauge~
Overall : Mid D6 in SM / Dan 10 Clear FINALLLLLLLLYYYYYYYYY
[ Still think my HR dan 9 is better ]
Speed : Low D6 around light 260s.
Consistency : This is one of my shittiest skillsets
Jacking : Low D7
Tech : Mid D6 worthy :X ME SUCK WITH STACKED SHIETS.
Long Notes : What is LN? Fail fest :^)
Stamina : Almost D7

~26th March 2016~ idk this is so old


~21st April 2016~ Break 6,000 PP


~26th July 2016~ When Galaxy Collpase & Blastix Riotz was a thing goddammit


~25th Aug 2016~


~26th Nov 2016~ 97.77% #777 LUL


I only play 4k. I do not have the motivation to learn anything else.

I'm relatively mundane and do not really talk much. I just play to de-stress mainly and just have the motivation for improvement I suppose.
About Me
I started playing VSRGs since the release of DJMAX ONLINE, way back at 2004.
Since then I grew interest with this genre of gaming and I went on playing every single DJMAX game from the PSP Versions.

So technically I have at least 390-ish days of my life spent playing VSRGs.

Despite all that, I'm still relatively horrible, LOL.

I only started 4k when i came into osu! after I was introduced by a schoolmate by it. Only found out about mania mode around September 2014.
I kinda gave up playing 5k 6k and 8k since osu!mania does not use much of these keycounts, its just mainly 4k and 7k.

Which of course forcved to to learn the whole game again, as I hated 4k from DJMAX, being extremely underwelming to play on.
[ Apart from Nightmare. The 1/3 Trip Jacks are F***ing atrocious to play with thumbs on the PSP. ]

I improved quite marginally i suppose throughout my 2 years + I have spent in 4k.
Still, in no way I am considered to be a high-tier player in my opinion. [ I don't play SM that often btw. ]
Achievements so Far
AiAe S Rank FINALLY

150 Jacking + rolls

149 1/8s Dumpstream

Stamina K.Y.A.F.A Why Zen Why

280 light, consistent 28-31kps

Shadows of Why is this even a thing


I GIVE UP PLAYING IN MWC AS I KNOW IM NOT GOOD ENOUGH. I HATE MYSELF. ( jkjk im cool with my shittiness )
